Clairview (south of Mackay) – bushfire as at 1.30pm Sun 23 Aug
Rural Fire Service (RFS) crews remain on scene at a bushfire burning south of Mackay in the Clairview area. The fire is located west of the Bruce Highway, adjacent to Clairview. Overnight, crews conducted backburning operations to contain the blaze. Crews are continuing to monitor the situation today. The fire is posing no threat to property at this time.
